1. Ant is used to build a project.
	To generate an executable -jar file "ant create_run_jar" command must be executed in the project directory
2. Above ant command will generate SCRUM.jar file. To run this and to enter the shell "java -jar SCRUM.jar" 
   must be called
3. The persistence used in this project is Sqlite. The automatic installation is not provided. Thus, for running the 
   project Sqlite must already be in the operating system. 
4. Testings are done with JUnit testing tool. All test methods are inside "test" source directory .

	